title: Rush - Clockwork Angels Tour (2013) FLAC
description:
Rush - Clockwork Angels Tour (Live) (2013) [FLAC]

Clockwork Angels Tour is a live album and film of Canadian progressive rock band Rush's Clockwork Angels Tour, released on November 19, 2013. The performances were selected from the band's shows in Phoenix, Dallas, and San Antonio (November 25, 28 and 30, 2012, respectively).
